15.text: Write a description about Sir Edmund Hillary, the first man to conquer Mount Everest using the given facts.

17.text: • became interested in mountain climbing while in secondary school

18.text: • worked in the Royal New Zealand air force as a navigator

19.text: • reached South Pole and later North Pole as part of the Commonwealth Trans-Atlantic Expedition

20.text: • the first person to reach the Poles and summit Everest

21.text: • reached the summit of Mount Everest on 29th May, 1953 with the help of the Nepalese Sherpa Tenzing Norgay – making them the first to summit Mt.Everest

22.text: • was awarded a Knighthood and Coronation medal by the Queen Elizabeth II, Padma Vibuhan posthumously by the Indian government in 2008 and many other awards
